'''挪威羊角號'''<ref>{{Cite |title=迪士尼新片《冰雪奇缘》受到挪威启发 |date=2014-01-23 |url=http://www.norway.org.cn/News_and_events/culture/film/Norway-became-the-Disney-movie-quotSnow-Romancequot-protagonist/ |accessdate= |publisher=挪威驻华大使馆 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323094250/http://norway.org.cn/news_and_events/culture/film/norway-became-the-disney-movie-quotsnow-romancequot-protagonist/ |archivedate=2016-03-23 |language=zh-cn |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=wm>{{Cite web |url=http://www.welchenmusic.com/prodshow.asp?ProdId=OZ052CD |title=NyeSongar.no - Karl Seglem |access-date=2015-03-22 |archive-date=2019-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612133542/http://www.welchenmusic.com/prodshow.asp?ProdId=OZ052CD |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>''bukke''是[[wikt:en:buck|buck]]的[[中古英語|中古英語]]可指「[[公羊|公羊]]」，現[[挪威語|挪威語]]與其關係密切的[[丹麥語|丹麥語]]僅作動詞「彎曲、[[鞠躬|鞠躬]]」，「bukkehorn」一詞殘留中古英語－中低地[[德語|德語]]的歷史痕跡。</ref>（{{lang-no|Bukkehorn}}），是[[挪威|挪威]][[民俗|民俗]][[樂器|樂器]]。具指孔可吹出旋律不同一般公羊號角（Billy Goat Horn），因此又稱'''羊角喇叭'''<ref>{{Cite|title=民间音乐|date=2009-09-06|url=http://www.norway.org.cn/About_Norway/culture/music1/folk|accessdate=|publisher=挪威驻华大使馆|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316065851/http://www.norway.org.cn/About_Norway/culture/music1/folk|archivedate=2013-03-16|language=zh-cn|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。製造材質通常取自五至七歲公羊羊角，原是高山夏季牧場的牧羊人發信號、管理牲畜或驅趕動物用途，後來鑿上指孔成為演奏樂器<ref>[http://home.online.no/~kgjetmun/page5.html Lur and Bukkehorn - Norwegian Folk Music] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030000341/http://home.online.no/~kgjetmun/page5.html |date=2015-10-30 }}</ref><ref name=linux>{{Cite |title=Bukkehorn - Billy Goat's Horn |date=2013-08-10 |url=http://linux.ofsdal.no/test/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/10-bukkehorn-Billy-Goat´s-horn.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate= |publisher=Steinar Ofsdal／A Fu（阿福） |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106011121/http://linux.ofsdal.no/test/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/10-bukkehorn-Billy-Goat%C2%B4s-horn.pdf |archivedate=2021-01-06 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

吹奏技巧分[[單簧管|單簧]]跟最常見[[小號|小號]]兩種方式，挪威男性演奏者卡爾·塞格林（{{link-en|Karl Seglem|Karl Seglem}}）{{r|wm}}<ref>[http://www.karlseglem.no/appbox/modules/cutecms/?key=biography Karl Seglem - biography] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403020931/http://www.karlseglem.no/appbox/modules/cutecms/?key=biography |date=2015-04-03 }}</ref>，以及參與[[迪士尼|迪士尼]]動畫電影《[[冰雪奇緣|冰雪奇緣]]》配樂的女性後進西絲兒·摩根·古洛（{{link-no|Sissel Morken Gullord|Sissel Morken Gullord}}）<ref>[http://gullord.no/index.php/en/my-work Sissel Morken Gullord - My work] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113212448/http://gullord.no/index.php/en/my-work |date=2013-11-13 }}</ref>等皆箇中翹楚。

